<li>Cluster&nbsp;- 134 node, 1608 Processor Cores and 6 TB of Memory</li>
<li>Performance&nbsp;- system performance of 16.5 Tera FLOPS. SMP Linpack of each node is 131 GFLOPS</li>
<li>Interconnects&nbsp;- Infiniband 4X QDR 40 Gbps networks and two Gigabit Ethernet networks</li>
<li>Storage&nbsp;- 24 Tera Byte Unified Storage using Lustre file system</li>
<li>Backup&nbsp;- Automated Tape Library with 8 LTO-4 drives and 77 media slots</li>
<li>Operating System&nbsp;- Red Hat Enterprise Linux 5.5</li>
